@{
    Layout = "_Layout";
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>UFOPay.io - Main</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/indexstyle.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.6.0/jquery.min.js"></script>

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

</head>

<body>
    <div class="content__first__side">
        <div class="content__demo">
            <p class="demo__msg">The project is under development, you see an interactive <span
                    style="font-weight: bold;">DEMO</span>
                version.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="welcome__info">
            <p class="welcome__msg__one">Accept and send payments <span style="color: #4d6cfa!important;">all over the
                    world</span></p>
            <p class="welcome__msg__two">Receive payments on the website, social networks or instant messengers from any
                country.</p>
            <a class="current__link__start" href="/register">Start accepting
                payments</a><span class="comission__msg">Commission from
                <span style="font-weight: bold;">0.7%</span></span>
        </div>
        <div class="welcome__image__content">
            <img class="welcome__img" src="./images/pages/wc_img.svg" alt="welcome_img">
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content__second__side">
        <div class="info__content">
            <p class="info__ask">What is our service suitable for?</p>

            <div class="answer__block">
                <div class="first__answer">
                    <svg class="svg_primary" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="48" width="48"
                        viewBox="0 0 48 48">
                        <path
                            d="M26 33.6q-.65 0-1.075-.425-.425-.425-.425-1.075 0-.65.425-1.075Q25.35 30.6 26 30.6h8q.65 0 1.075.425.425.425.425 1.075 0 .65-.425 1.075-.425.425-1.075.425Zm-12.05-1.25q-.45-.45-.425-1.05.025-.6.425-1.05l4.1-4.15-4.1-4.15q-.45-.45-.45-1.05 0-.6.45-1.05.45-.45 1.05-.45.6 0 1.05.45l5.2 5.2q.25.25.325.5.075.25.075.55 0 .3-.075.55-.075.25-.325.5l-5.2 5.2q-.45.45-1.05.45-.6 0-1.05-.45ZM7 40q-1.2 0-2.1-.9Q4 38.2 4 37V11q0-1.2.9-2.1Q5.8 8 7 8h34q1.2 0 2.1.9.9.9.9 2.1v26q0 1.2-.9 2.1-.9.9-2.1.9Zm0-3h34V15.2H7V37Z">
                        </path>
                    </svg>
                    <p style="color: #000; margin-bottom: 20px;">Integration</p>
                    <p> Solve complex business problems with a simple <span style="color:#4d6cfa;">API</span>.
                        Everything you need to accept payments.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="second__answer">
                    <svg class="svg_primary" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="48" width="48"
                        viewBox="0 0 48 48">
                        <path
                            d="M6 42v-7.8l9.7-9.7-8.95-9q-.45-.45-.675-1-.225-.55-.225-1.1t.225-1.1q.225-.55.675-1l4.5-4.55q.45-.45 1-.675.55-.225 1.1-.225t1.125.225q.575.225 1.025.675l9 9 9.85-9.85q.25-.25.5-.325.25-.075.55-.075.3 0 .55.075.25.075.5.325l5.65 5.65q.25.25.325.5.075.25.075.55 0 .3-.075.55-.075.25-.325.5l-9.85 9.85 9 9q.45.45.675 1.025.225.575.225 1.125t-.225 1.1q-.225.55-.675 1l-4.5 4.45q-.45.45-1 .675-.55.225-1.1.225t-1.1-.225q-.55-.225-1-.675l-9-8.95L13.8 42Zm11.85-19.65 4.5-4.5-3.65-3.65-2.4 2.4-2.1-2.1 2.4-2.4-3.2-3.2-4.5 4.5Zm16.7 16.75 4.5-4.5-3.2-3.2-2.4 2.4-2.1-2.1 2.4-2.4-3.65-3.65-4.5 4.5ZM9 39h3.5l20.75-20.75-3.5-3.5L9 35.5Zm26.35-22.85 3.5-3.5-3.5-3.5-3.5 3.5Z">
                        </path>
                    </svg>
                    <p style="color: #000; margin-bottom: 20px;">Provision of services</p>
                    <p>Do you teach a foreign language? You no longer need a bank terminal. Show the QR code to your
                        client and the funds will instantly be credited to your card.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="third__answer">
                    <svg class="svg_primary" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="48" width="48"
                        viewBox="0 0 48 48">
                        <path
                            d="M32 22q.85 0 1.425-.575Q34 20.85 34 20q0-.85-.575-1.425Q32.85 18 32 18q-.85 0-1.425.575Q30 19.15 30 20q0 .85.575 1.425Q31.15 22 32 22Zm-14.5-5h7q.65 0 1.075-.425Q26 16.15 26 15.5q0-.65-.425-1.075Q25.15 14 24.5 14h-7q-.65 0-1.075.425Q16 14.85 16 15.5q0 .65.425 1.075Q16.85 17 17.5 17Zm-6 25q-1.05 0-1.975-.7T8.3 39.6q-1.25-4.3-2.075-7.425Q5.4 29.05 4.9 26.7q-.5-2.35-.7-4.175Q4 20.7 4 19q0-4.6 3.2-7.8T15 8h10q1.35-1.8 3.425-2.9Q30.5 4 33 4q1.25 0 2.125.875T36 7q0 .3-.075.6t-.175.55q-.2.55-.375 1.1t-.275 1.2L39.65 15h2.85q.65 0 1.075.425Q44 15.85 44 16.5v11.35q0 .5-.275.9t-.775.55l-4.6 1.5-2.7 9.05q-.3 1-1.1 1.575t-1.8.575H27q-1.25 0-2.125-.875T24 39v-1h-4v1q0 1.25-.875 2.125T17 42Zm-.25-3H17v-4h10v4h5.75l3.15-10.5 5.1-1.75V18h-2.6L32 11.6q.05-.85.275-2.075Q32.5 8.3 32.9 6.8q-2.15.55-3.8 1.65-1.65 1.1-2.4 2.55H15q-3.3 0-5.65 2.35Q7 15.7 7 19q0 2.1 1.1 7.325T11.25 39ZM24 22.9Z">
                        </path>
                    </svg>
                    <p style="color: #000; margin-bottom: 20px;">Donations</p>
                    <p>Stream your parties? Get donations by adding a payment link to the stream description. Don't
                        worry about which country or bank the transfer is coming from. No recalls, payments, and no
                        expectations.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content__third__side">
        <div class="comm__questions">
            <span class="comm__header">Frequently Asked Questions</span>
            <div class="first__comm__question">
                <p class="first__comm__title">How does it work?</p>
                <div class="first__comm__answer" style="display: none; margin-top: 35px; color: #000;">
                    <p>The service detects the card issuer and sends simultaneous requests for authorization and
                        crediting to your balance in encrypted form, providing information control over transaction
                        statuses.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="second__comm__question">
                <p class="second__comm__title">Can I pay with my phone?</p>
                <div class="second__comm__answer" style="display: none; margin-top: 35px; color: #000;">
                    <p>Yes. The transaction takes place through the Internet browser of any device, including a
                        smartphone.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="third__comm__question">
                <p class="third__comm__title">Is it safe?</p>
                <div class="third__comm__answer" style="display: none; margin-top: 35px; color: #000;">
                    <p>Yes. Data is securely protected and encrypted in accordance with the PCI DSS 3.2 Level 1 security
                        certificate.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        $(document).ready(function () {
            $(".first__comm__question").click(function () {
                $(".first__comm__answer").slideToggle();
            });
        });
        $(document).ready(function () {
            $(".second__comm__question").click(function () {
                $(".second__comm__answer").slideToggle();
            });
        });
        $(document).ready(function () {
            $(".third__comm__question").click(function () {
                $(".third__comm__answer").slideToggle();
            });
        });
    </script>

</body>

</html>